Surveillance technology : A prospering technology
Radio-frequency identification is a technology which uses a wireless non-contact system to scan and transfer the data from a tag attached to people or products from radio-frequency electromagnetic fields .
After this , it can automatically get the identification and tracking .
Nowadays , this technology has been used in many kinds of fields , such as transportation and logistics , transportation payment , product tracking and inventory systems , some institutions and so on .
More interestingly , this technology is being used in human identification , even planting the chip into human bodies .
This fact becomes very controversial among people and the possibility of personal information released without knowing also brought the public 's concerns .
In some fields , surveillance technology does have brought us tremendous benefit and advantage .
Logistics and transportation are major areas of utilization of RFID technology .
In the transportation , almost all of the people have transport cards for daily transport .
Since we do not bring cash to pay for the transportation fees , enormous time has been saved for everybody .
For a society , there will be a more efficient transportation system .
For the logistics , if all the products are attached to the tag , it is much easier to count and record all the products .
This would make the logistics process more effective and also prevent the occurrence of product lost because of the tracking .
Since the inventory management is very important for some kind of companies , this technology is playing a very significant role .
The super markets are also using this technology to tag their products , which can record the conditions of all of the products in time and prevent of stealing .
When checking out , the price tag will be scanned to get the total payment very quickly .
This will save customers time and also improve the profit of the market .
The library also use this technology to identify the membership of the people enter , which ensures the security and the member itself would also conserve their information made in this library .
Both the library and museum applying this technology to avoid some belongings were taken out illegally .
In some kindergarten , the RFID is used to tab the children to keep a record of their attendance and whereabouts .
On the condition that the kindergarten students are very young and they do not have a very sound self-conscious , this system could prevent them from losing .
All in all , an RFID system being used to catch the information about the object and track .
This function could be used in many aspects .
By RFID , a customer who is potential to buying a very expensive luxury will be less reluctant to consider what if it lost , because the RFID can help them get it back .
This will inversely improve the sale in the shop .
Although in many respects , this technology can be used for positive and evidently beneficial ways , in some areas it is so controversial .
The most controversial part may be a human identification .
It probably can be divided into several types .
The first type is just say the ID card which are carried externally on the person .
By using this card , our identities could be confirmed and the information about a certain institutions can be kept .
However , this will raise the privacy protection issues .
How can it be guaranteed that our information would not be abused ?
Maybe this part can be resolved by using another technology .
For example , the ID cards could be implanted into a switch which can be controlled by the owner .
When not using it , just switch off the cards , then it would be just a useless paper .
Another human identification are implanting RFID chips into human bodies .
For this part , not only the privacy problem is concerned , but the human health .
Does the implant chip definitely safe and feasible ?
Will it affect the normal functionality of the other organs ?
All of these problems are waiting to be resolved .
In solution , surveillance technology has been used for a much broader area .
Some have been widely accepted by the public but some were not .
Actually , this technology is very useful and should be definitely going to be used .
What should be concerned is how it can be applied in the right area in the right way .
If there is some controversy , how it can be improved .
Only if it is made use of a wise and sensible approach and be adjusted and refined very profoundly , can it bring us the maximize benefits .
