For this kind of situation , RAID will help a lot .
Actually , not only for scientific observations but also during adventure journeys or travelling , RFID can defend human beings from harm .
Firstly , knowing where the travelers are and may go can assist them to know what the surroundings will be like and they can prepare better to protect themselves or they can change direction to avoid a potential danger .
Furthermore , by telling the geographical position of the people , RFID could accelerate the rescue process and will improve the survival rate of the victims .
