Firstly , for scientific exploration , rescue and police events , the privacy factor is far less important than the individual or social safety and scientific results .
In addition , by observation journeys and travel , we only need to use RFID to some certain individuals and they will agree with this action for their own benefit .
Above all , I think we could not ban the use of RFID completely , since it will be of great help in human 's benefit during scientific exploration , rescue and police events .
